# javascript-for-ethical-hacking
day1 
  install kali linux in your respected system.
  for windows use the virtual box and for mac use the utm
  in utm you could use the pre installed kali by accessing the gallery
  once done with the installation do update.
  once updation is done configure the dvwa
           use cmd:- sudo docker run --rm -it -d -p 127.0.0.1:8080:80 vulnerable/web-dvwa 

  install the code-oss to have proper accessing to the ssh ports to run dockers if needed
           use cmd:- sudo apt install open-ssh
  
  once its done confiugure the the owasp juice shop
           use the cmd:- sudo docker run --rm -it -d -p 127.0.0.1:3000:3000 bkimminich/juice-shop 


  note the cmds might change with the cersions getting added to it, so kindly look it, if errors runs use the documentation or --help.

  thtas for the day day.
